{"tid":552423,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果耶穌見到平安谷班人想用石頭掟死簡淑兒，佢會點做？","createTime":"2018-02-06T13:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T01:50:12.000Z","uid":89046,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7238d8796f20c1ce6270f4e021b53fb2c5a4b3","tid":552423,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ddfe771a82574a7ef67633079dd7a6f0c61ba7","tid":552423,"uid":162043,"like":85,"dislike":5,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"佢會屌死哂睇tbb班戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3ff60725d36975a622152f48e78aab54347433","tid":552423,"uid":89046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"約翰福音 第八章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374a85d051726234bc3fadcaefe123c7eb87ca81","tid":552423,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"饒恕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a011a70333e7cbb8ad49586c382f1ce28ae91d0b","tid":552423,"uid":52605,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"谷爺話 你個外人阻住我哋執行鄉例 大家用石頭掟埋佢"},{"pid":"8fef97f996b3e17c4bed43906f346e3682d3de73","tid":552423,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b89d2bc48e2015e53707c444aa0a05d26647d9","tid":552423,"uid":89046,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"7b3ff60725d36975a622152f48e78aab54347433","tid":552423,"uid":89046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"約翰福音 第八章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:25:49.000Z","msg":"1：於是各人都回家去了；耶穌卻往橄欖山去，清早又回到殿裡。眾百姓都到他那裡去，他就坐下，教訓他們。<br />\n<br />\n2：文士和法利賽人帶著一個行淫時被拿的婦人來，叫他站在當中，就對耶穌說：夫子，這婦人是正行淫之時被拿的。<br />\n<br />\n3：<span style=\"color: red;\">摩西在律法上吩咐我們把這樣的婦人用石頭打死。</span>你說該把他怎麼樣呢？<br />\n<br />\n4：他們說這話，乃試探耶穌，要得著告他的把柄。耶穌卻彎著腰，用指頭在地上畫字。<br />\n<br />\n5：他們還是不住的問他，耶穌就直起腰來，對他們說：<span style=\"color: orange;\">你們中間誰是沒有罪的，誰就可以先拿石頭打他。</span><br />\n<br />\n6：於是又彎著腰，用指頭在地上畫字。<br />\n<br />\n7：<span style=\"color: orange;\">他們聽見這話，就從老到少，一個一個的都出去了</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只剩下耶穌一人，還有那婦人仍然站在當中。<br />\n<br />\n8：耶穌就直起腰來，對他說：婦人，那些人在哪裡呢？沒有人定你的罪嗎？<br />\n<br />\n9：他說：主啊，沒有。耶穌說：我也不定你的罪。去吧，從此不要再犯罪了！<br />\n<br />\n10：耶穌又對眾人說：我是世界的光。跟從我的，就不在黑暗裡走，必要得著生命的光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397deb14700f2c4b4005bf8658e523002afe3a50","tid":552423,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e066562a065a30df33309dcd904a35d1476ce6d3","tid":552423,"uid":170044,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"耶穌只會叫你捐錢俾佢"},{"pid":"8ce7adf09e6aca499800dfec56e7068c92ca44b9","tid":552423,"uid":89046,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e066562a065a30df33309dcd904a35d1476ce6d3","tid":552423,"uid":170044,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"耶穌只會叫你捐錢俾佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:42:40.000Z","msg":"賣贖罪券"},{"pid":"269c0675bf9ccf7b7f8fe4c94b4e9010ae7cc45d","tid":552423,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fcaf29cc47a34676a45059d5a34a05dc9ee657","tid":552423,"uid":96743,"like":8,"dislike":24,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"唔係撐<br />\n但天主教同耶教係唔同既<br />\n贖罪卷 奶共教宗都係天主教<br />\n同耶蘇